utils

Do You Need It?
Yes, if your app has multiple pages and you want consistent styles.
For a small app with basic styling, you can manage this directly in main.dart.

models

Do You Need It?
Yes, if your app has complex data (like storing or retrieving reminders from a database or API).
If reminders are simple (e.g., only managed in memory), you can skip this for now.


widgets

Do You Need It?
Yes, if buttons in your app share a consistent style.
For unique button styles on each screen, you can skip this.






